# Figma Personal Access Token (File content Read + Variables Read)
# Used by tooling/figma-sync for headless variable sync (`pnpm figma:sync`).
# Create at https://www.figma.com/developers/api#access-tokens — do not commit the real value.
FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN=

# --- Interactive Figma MCP (no env var) ---
# For figma-console / Desktop Bridge tools (screenshots, execute, etc.):
# 1. Open the CADS file in Figma Desktop
# 2. Plugins → Development → Figma Desktop Bridge
# 3. Bridge connects to ws://localhost:9225 automatically
# Official Figma MCP Code Connect maps can also use figma.code-connect.json in this repo.
